Template: openstack/title
Type: title
Description: OpenStack Config Helper

Template: openstack/node_type
Type: select
Choices: Controller, Compute, Volume, Customize
Default: Controller 
Description: What is this host?
  Choose host type
   * Controller host: Cloud Controller installed
   * Compute    host: Compute Node installed (VMs are on this host)
   * Volume     host: Volume Host
   * Customize  : Customize 

Template: openstack/service_host
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: Please enter Controller host ip

Template: openstack/glance_host
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: Please enter Glance host ip

Template: openstack/keystone_host
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: Please enter Keystone host ip

Template: openstack/service_password
Type: password
Default: openstack
Description: enter a password
 Enter a service password here.  Service password is used by openstack daemons.

Template: openstack/admin_password
Type: password
Default: openstack
Description: enter a password
 Enter a admin password here. Admin password is used by administrator

Template: openstack/mysql_host
Type: string
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: enter a host
 Enter a mysql host ${user}

Template: openstack/mysql_user
Type: string
Default: nova
Description: enter a user
 Enter a mysql user

Template: openstack/mysql_password
Type: password
Default: openstack
Description: enter a password
 Enter a mysql password here.

Template: openstack/rabbit_host
Type: string 
Default: 127.0.0.1
Description: enter a password
 Enter a rabbit host.

Template: openstack/rabbit_password
Type: password
Default: openstack
Description: enter a password
 Enter a rabbit password.

Template: openstack/libvirt_type
Type: select
Choices: KVM, LXC
Default: KVM 
Description: Choose virtualization type

Template: openstack/net_man
Type: select
Choices: FlatManager, FlatDHCPManager, VlanManager, QuantumManager
Default: FlatDHCPManager 
Description:  Choose network type
 Choose network model 
  * Flat
  * FlatDHCP
  * Vlan
  * Quantum

Template: openstack/public_interface
Type: string
Default: br100
Description:  Interface for public IP addresses

Template: openstack/vlan_interface
Type: select
Choices: ${interfaces} 
Description:  Interface for vlan

Template: openstack/fixed_ragne
Type: string
Default: 10.0.0.0/24
Description: Please enter network cidr
 This installer setup a network. Please enter cider for the network

Template: openstack/floating_range
Type: string
Default: 10.0.100.0/24
Description: Please enter floating network cidr
 This cidr is used for floating ips

Template: openstack/setup_database
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Do you want setup dbs?
 Waring: If yes, databases are dropped.

Template: openstack/enabled_services
Type: multiselect
Choices: g-api, g-reg, key, n-api, n-crt, n-obj, n-cpu, n-net, n-vol, n-sch, n-novnc, n-xvnc, n-cauth, horizon, mysql, rabbit
Default: g-api, g-reg, key, n-api, n-crt, n-obj, n-cpu, n-net, n-vol, n-sch, n-novnc, n-xvnc, n-cauth, horizon, mysql, rabbit
Description: please select enabled services

Template: openstack/install_note
Type: note
Description: Configuration and package selection is finished.
 In order to finish installation please run openstack-install
